<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>They both have bars, the same categories, labels, etc.</li>
      <li>One counts by ones for the scale and the other counts by twos (call this out as 
        <q>scaling</q> ).
      </li>
      <li>The 12 on the first graph goes higher than the 12 in the second graph.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


